=== Network / Wifi ===
The wifi is configured via wpa_supplicnat if you use WPA2 in your network.
Add to {{Path|/etc/conf.d/modules}}:

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/conf.d/net|lang=bash|1=
modules=( "wpa_supplicant" )
wpa_supplicant_wlan0="-Dwext"
config_wlan0=( "dhcp" )
}}

